th\'fby\'ec: qhe m\'e2 h\'ea\u660? qo, n\u603?\u768?-\'e1 t\'ed qo ch\u601?\u768? t\'f9 q\'f4\u660?-ma.\par
c\'e0bo: chi t\'ea g\u776?\u616?\u768? k\'e0\u660? c\'e0-n\u596?-pa\u772? qhe ve yo.\par
