c\'e0bo: h\u603? q\u596?\u770? p\u601?\u768? ph\u601?\u770?\u660? a l\'e2 o.\par
c\'e0m\'e1: h\u603? chi \u596?\u772? qhe \u331?\'e0 d\u596?\u770? a\u772? ve t\'ed qhe qo n\'ee \'9a\'ed g\u776?a q\u596?\u770? h\u603?\u769?. n\'ee \'9a\'ed \u331?\'e2 ni.\par
