c\'e0bo: \u331?\'e0 k\'e0\u660? qhe d\u596?\u770? a\u772? ve y\'f2 q\'f4\u660?-ma. \u331?\'e0 ve k\'e0\u660? m\'e2 g\u776?a ph\u601?\u770?\u660? a-ni \'9ae\u772? q\'f4\u660?-ma. l\'e0 chi. y\'e0\u660?-qh\'e2 q\u596?\u768?\u660? l\'e0 m\'e2 g\u776?a ph\u601?\u770?\u660? ve a-k\u603?\u769?, \u331?\'e0 d\u596?\u770? ve \u596?\u772?, chi qhe d\u596?\u770? l\u603? q\'f4\u660?-ma: l\'e0 m\'e2 c\u596?\u768? ve l\'e0 c\u596?\u768? ve a-k\u603?\u769? l\u603? \u596?\u772? m\'e2 c\u596?\u768? ve a-c\'ed \u603?\u768?\u660? q\u596?\u770?\u660? d\u596?\u770? ha\u772? t\'f9 c\u596?\u768? d\u596?\u770? l\u603?. h\u603? q\u596?\u770? p\u601?\u768? l\u603? ph\u601?\u770?\u660? a-t\u603?\u768? te ve y\'f2.\par
c\'e0m\'e1: \u331?\'e0 ve ha-pa t\'ea m\'e0 l\u603? t\'ea chi \u331?\'e2 ni g\u776?a q\u596?\u770? \'9a\u596?\u772? h\u603?\u769? q\'f4\u660?-ma. qhe q\u596?\u770? a qo, p\u601?\u768? qo ph\u601?\u770?\u660? a-t\u603?\u768? d\u596?\u770? a\u772? ve y\'f2, \u331?\'e0 k\'e0\u660?.\par
