: l\'e0 kho n\u603?\u769? \u596?\u772? \'e2 ph\u596?\u770? ph\u596?\u770? \u603?\u768?\u660? ve q\'f4\u660? p\'ee\u660?.\par
 c\'e0bo: l\'e0 kho q\'f4\u660? ve k\'e0\u660? n\'e1 qh\u603? n\'e1 b\u616?\u768? qhe te t\u603? a ve y\'f2.\par
